---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/sections/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/sections/Footer.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/button/Button.astro';
---

<html lang="en" data-theme="dark" class="dark">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Instagram Reel Framing Tool — Case Study"
      description="Case study for a web-based internal tool designed to speed up social media video formatting and export."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <Button href="/portfolio" variant="outline" size="sm">← Back to Projects</Button>
      </div>

      <section class="card-surface p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--accent)] mb-3">Case Study</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-foreground m-0">Instagram Reel Framing Tool</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          A web-based internal content production tool designed to make social media video formatting faster, cleaner and more consistent.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Project Type</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">Internal Tool</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Role</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">Concept & Workflow Design</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Tools</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">FFmpeg, Web UI</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Year</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-8 border-[color:var(--border)]" />

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Overview</h2>
            <p>
              This project was built to simplify a repetitive part of content production: taking a raw video,
              formatting it correctly for Instagram, adding a visual frame, and exporting a polished result ready for publishing.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Problem</h2>
            <p>
              Preparing social media videos manually usually means adjusting aspect ratios, aligning composition,
              adding visual structure, and exporting multiple versions before the content feels ready.
              That process takes time and creates unnecessary friction in content production.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Goal</h2>
            <p>
              The goal was to create a lightweight tool that reduces repetitive editing work while keeping the final output
              visually clean and suitable for Instagram publishing.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Approach</h2>
            <p>
              I focused on a simple upload-based workflow: the user uploads a video, the tool detects the best usable format,
              applies a styled frame, and prepares an export-ready result through FFmpeg-powered processing.
              The priority was usability, speed, and consistency.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Outcome</h2>
            <p>
              The tool turned a repetitive manual process into a faster workflow and reduced video preparation time
              by around 70% in personal use. More importantly, it demonstrated how a small internal tool can solve a real content production problem.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">What This Project Shows</h2>
            <p>
              This case study reflects a product-thinking approach: identifying a real workflow bottleneck,
              designing a simple solution, and using technology to improve execution speed in a marketing-related process.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <Button href="https://instagram-reels-maker-production.up.railway.app/instagram-frame.html" variant="primary" size="sm">Open Live Tool</Button>
          <Button href="/portfolio" variant="secondary" size="sm">Back to Projects</Button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
